{"word":"λυτρόω","slug":"λυτρόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>λυτρόω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:λύτρον\">λύτρον</a></el>] <b>to redeem/ransom,</b> in commercial sense <b><a href='B:670 1:18'>1 Pt 1:18</a>,</b> otherwise in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ transf.\">transf.</a> sense of deliverance <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fr.\">fr.</a> an oppressive or destructive condition<b>,</b> and only <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <b><a href='B:490 24:21'>Lk 24:21</a>; <a href='B:510 28:19'>Ac 28:19</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:630 2:14'>Tit 2:14</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:λύτρον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:λύτρωσις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}